snippet.title: Rappelz - Epic 9.1: Masquerade Trailer
snippet.description:
Epic 9.1 Rappelz: Masquerade has finally been released! Skill rebalancing, new dungeon, enhancement system, level cap increase, new weapons and more! 
Download the game and become a hero in Rappelz - a free-to-play dark fantasy MMORPG! http://en.rappelz.webzen.com/
